verbose_text: Two-way ANOVA analysis followed by Bonferroni post hoc analysis showed that IL-1RA did not reduce circulating chemokines in ME7 animals : There were no significant main effects or interactions for CXCL1, and while there was an interaction between disease and treatment for CCL2 (F 1,12 = 13.39, p = 0.003), Bonferroni post hoc analysis showed that CCL2 was not different between ME7 + LPS and ME7 + LPS + IL-1RA.
evidence: IL-1RA did not reduce circulating chemokines
